nsfw.value: :underage: Materials which display explicit or suggestive sexual or gory content. Content or media inappropriate for general audience, professional, or educational settings.

scam.value: :money_mouth: Intent to obtain account information, personally identifiable information, or solicitation of a service or product with no intention to fulfill such action.

spam.value: :mailbox_with_no_mail: Repeated messages or link advertisements with intent to clutter or disrupt normal proceedings in a channel.

altr.value: :busts_in_silhouette: Use of an alternative or secondary account to bypass mute or ban.
